OL,3,CLondon bus drivers have 'borne the
OL,4,Cbrunt' of extreme heat in the city
OL,6,FLondon's bus drivers have 'borne the
OL,7,Fbrunt' of the extreme heat in the
OL,8,Fcity, a Labour MP said, as she urged
OL,9,Fmore to be done about climate change
OL,10,Fto improve the transport system.
OL,12,FFeryal Clark, who represents Enfield
OL,13,FNorth, addressed the Minister for
OL,14,FRoads and Buses in the Commons and
OL,15,Fsaid London's mayor was working with
OL,16,Foperators to help protect drivers.
OL,18,FITV News London has highlighted how
OL,19,Fdrivers can work in extreme heat in
OL,20,Fcabs as hot as 40 Celsius.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
