OL,3,CLondon bus drivers have 'borne the
OL,4,Cbrunt' of extreme heat in the city
OL,6,FSadiq Khan previously said drivers
OL,7,Fshould not risk their personal safety
OL,8,Fand "must stop" if their bus is too
OL,9,Fhot and not worry about following
OL,10,Ftheir usual timetable.
OL,12,FSpeaking in the Commons today, Simon
OL,13,FLightwood, Minister for Roads and
OL,14,FBuses said: "I will of course join my
OL,15,Fhonourable friend in commending the
OL,16,FMayor of London for the work that he's
OL,17,Fdoing to keep the people that power
OL,18,Four transport system safe.
OL,20,F"A well functioning transport system
OL,21,Fis integral to growth."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
