OL,3,CLondon bus drivers have 'borne the
OL,4,Cbrunt' of extreme heat in the city
OL,6,FResponding to Feryal Clark's comment
OL,7,Fabout climate change, he added:
OL,8,F"Whilst we continue to decarbonise the
OL,9,Fthe transport system, we must also
OL,10,Fensure that it is resilient to the
OL,11,Fimpacts of climate change.
OL,13,F"The Government has published its
OL,14,FClimate Adaptation Strategy for
OL,15,FTransport which sets out our vision
OL,16,Ffor a climate resilient transport
OL,17,Fsystem that underpins growth, keeps
OL,18,Fpeople and goods moving and supports
OL,19,Fevery part of the UK economy."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
