OL,3,CLondon bus drivers have 'borne the
OL,4,Cbrunt' of extreme heat in the city
OL,6,FBus drivers have previously called on
OL,7,FTransport for London and bus companies
OL,8,Fto introduce a series of protections
OL,9,Fin their contracts that they say would
OL,10,Fhelp make their jobs safer and improve
OL,11,Fthe way they work.
OL,13,FThe London Assembly agreed a motion
OL,14,Ffor a 'Bill of Rights' that would see
OL,15,Fcontractual protections for drivers,
OL,16,Fincluding:
OL,18,FThe rights would include:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
