OL,3,CLondon bus drivers have 'borne the
OL,4,Cbrunt' of extreme heat in the city
OL,6,FLorna Murphy, TfL's Director of Buses,
OL,7,Fsaid: "Bus drivers play an essential
OL,8,Frole in keeping the capital moving.
OL,10,F"Alongside bus operators, we take
OL,11,Ftheir safety and welfare seriously and
OL,12,Fwe rightly require operators to meet
OL,13,Fhigh standards."
